Here are paste-ready photorealistic prompts you can use in Nano Banana (or similar image models). Pick one scene or mix details from two prompts.

Hotels
Prompt:
Photorealistic urban hotel lobby during check-in rush, marble floor reflectance and layered seating groups, front-desk associate handing a keycard folder to a guest (both in profile, faces not toward camera), warm pendant clusters mixed with cool daylight from revolving doors, luggage cart and floral arrangement in foreground bokeh, candid hospitality documentary tone, no property name on signage, no readable rate screens, no loyalty program logos in focus.

Shot on full-frame DSLR, 85mm or 35mm, f/5.6–f/8 for clarity, Adobe neutral profile, minimal oversharpening, natural chromatic aberration, real-world imperfections, documentary editorial style.


